OL,3,CMan jailed for three years after XL
OL,4,CBully dog attacked 12-year-old girl
OL,6,FAn Ebbw Vale man, whose dog attacked a
OL,7,F12-year-old girl has received a
OL,8,Fsentence of three years in prison.
OL,10,FJustin Allison, 38, appeared at
OL,11,FNewport Crown Court on Wednesday 29
OL,12,FJanuary after previously pleading
OL,13,Fguilty to possessing a banned breed
OL,14,Fwithout a licence and being in charge
OL,15,Fof a dog dangerously out of control in
OL,16,Fa public place.
OL,18,FHe also admitted a charge of
OL,19,Fpossessing an offensive weapon in a
OL,20,Fprivate place.
