OL,3,CMan jailed for three years after XL
OL,4,CBully dog attacked 12-year-old girl
OL,6,FOfficers were called to an address in
OL,7,FThe Crescent, Nantyglo, in October
OL,8,Fafter reports of a dog attack on a
OL,9,Fchild.
OL,11,FThe dog, which was later identified as
OL,12,Fan XL Bully, was seized and humanely
OL,13,Fdestroyed by a veterinary surgeon. The
OL,14,Fdog was also unregistered by Allison.
OL,16,FFollowing a number of attacks on
OL,17,Fpeople it has been a criminal offence
OL,18,Fto own an XL bully in England and
OL,19,FWales without an exemption certificate
OL,20,Fsince February last year.
