OL,3,CMan jailed for three years after XL
OL,4,CBully dog attacked 12-year-old girl
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector for Gwent
OL,7,FPolice, Virginia Davies, who was the
OL,8,Fsenior investigating officer, said:
OL,9,F"Allison failed to keep his dog under
OL,10,Fcontrol and a girl was viciously
OL,11,Fattacked, causing serious injuries. We
OL,12,Fwish her the very best with her
OL,13,Fongoing recovery following this attack.
OL,15,F"This case should serve as a reminder
OL,16,Fto all dog owners of the importance of
OL,17,Fhaving your dog under control at all
OL,18,Ftimes.
