OL,4,CBully dog attacked 12-year-old girl
OL,6,F"We take all reports of suspected
OL,7,Firresponsible dog ownership seriously
OL,8,Fand we urge everyone to follow the
OL,9,Flegislation and guidance to prevent
OL,10,Fevents like this happening in the
OL,11,Ffuture."
OL,13,FThe 12-year-old required hospital
OL,14,Ftreatment for her injuries following
OL,15,Fthe attack. Allison was jailed for
OL,16,Fthree years and banned from owning
OL,17,Fdogs for 10 years.
